1.title: Here We Go Again
1.plot: Nathan threatens Jenelle with felony charges. Leah gets sad news about Ali while waiting to hear if she'll lose custody of the twins. Kailyn tries to rebuild her relationship with Jo but hurts things with Javi. Chelsea faces Adam at Aubree's first day of kindergarten.

2.title: In the Dark
2.plot: When Nathan takes Kaiser on an unexpected trip, Jenelle tries to charge him with kidnapping. Leah anxiously awaits word from the court but Corey receives the verdict of their custody case. Kailyn gets surprising news about Javi's job. Adam threatens to take Chelsea back to court for custody of Aubree.

3.title: Breaking Apart
3.plot: Leah receives the verdict of her custody case. A huge fight destroys Kailyn and Jo's renewed friendship. Jenelle introduces her new boyfriend to Barb. Chelsea is outraged by something Adam posts online.

4.title: Iced Out
4.plot: Kailyn and Javi receive bad news about his job; Leah is upset with Corey for confusing the girls about the custody arrangement; Barb worries about Jenelle's new boyfriend; and Chelsea and Cole take a major step.

5.title: No Access
5.plot: Cole has a big surprise for Chelsea. Kailyn reveals a huge secret that's been weighing on her and Javi. Jenelle is forced to face her assault charges against Nathan's girlfriend.

6.title: Hindsight
6.plot: Leah flirts with the idea of getting back with Jeremy. Isaac struggles with Javi's impending deployment. Jenelle's birthday trip to New York turns sour after hearing from Nathan. Chelsea and Cole celebrate their engagement, but Aubree has some sad news about Adam.

7.title: Man of the House
7.plot: Javi says a tearful goodbye to his family before deployment. Jenelle meets with Nathan, fueling David's jealousy. Corey and Leah face off at Ali's doctor's appointment. Chelsea and Cole debate changing Aubree's last name.

8.title: Didn't Mean It
8.plot: Leah and Corey battle in court over custody of the twins. Jenelle agrees to let Nathan see Kaiser and David volunteers to be their contact person. Kail struggles to help Isaac while he misses Javi.

9.title: While You Were Out
9.plot: Barbara and David face off over Jenelle, leading to a 911 call. Aubree gets a new accessory. Kailyn and Javi struggle with his deployment. Leah gets troubling news about custody.

10.title: Choose Your Battles
10.plot: Kailyn tries to repair her relationship with Vee. Cole escorts Aubree to her father/daughter dance. Some mysterious medical ailments force Jenelle to seek help in New York. Leah and Corey's coparenting is shattered by a disturbing video.

11.title: Turn the Page
11.plot: Jenelle's medical woes lead to a disastrous fight with Barbara. Leah and Miranda make amends. Aubree drops a big question on Adam. Kailyn rebuilds her relationship with Jo but distances herself from Javi.

12.title: Gone Fishing
12.plot: An emotional meltdown over Barb ruins Jenelle's fun day with her sons.. Kailyn and Javi's marriage is dangerously close to divorce. Chelsea celebrates milestones with Aubree. Just when Leah and Corey start to get along, her relationship with Jeremy breaks down.

13.title: Breaking the Wall
13.plot: Jenelle faces Nathan and his girlfriend in court for her assault trial. Aubree goes dress shopping for Chelsea and Cole's wedding, while Adam airs some frustrations. Jeremy has to leave town, much to Addie and Leah's dismay

14.title: Deja Vu
14.plot: Leah struggles with Addie missing her father. Chelsea meets with Adam's ex. Jenelle and Nathan face off in court over custody of Kaiser. Kailyn starts summer school with some extra help from Jo.

15.plot: Nessa and the moms dish on never-before-seen moments and take a trip down memory lane with each of their children.

16.title: Homecoming
16.plot: Javi returns home from deployment to mixed reactions. After a flood devastates West Virginia, Jeremy and Leah have trouble communicating. Chelsea hopes her doctor's visit goes well so she can finally make the baby announcement

17.title: Privacy Please
17.plot: Jenelle and David keep some big news under wraps. Kailyn and Javi adjust to their new relationship. Jeremy isn't happy about Leah's vacation plans. Chelsea finds out Adam is behind on child support.

18.title: Heartache
18.plot: avi and Kailyn get into a huge fight after he shows up unannounced. Jenelle tries to keep her pregnancy a secret from Barbara. Chelsea and Cole question postponing their wedding.

19.title: Last to Know
19.plot: Jenelle reveals her pregnancy to Barbara and Jace. Aubree starts first grade. Jo co-parents Isaac with both Kailyn and Javi. Leah and her daughters take a girls trip to California.

20.title: Fake Out
20.plot: Leah receives some surprise news from Ali's doctor about Aleeah. Jenelle thinks Nathan is trying to win her back and David isn't having it. Kailyn and Isaac start school but the added pressure causes strife between Jo and Vee.

21.title: I Don't Wanna Talk About It
21.plot: Jenelle prepares for her upcoming court date after getting some surprising news about Nathan. Chelsea celebrates Aubree's 7th birthday. Jeremy returns home from South Dakota. Kailyn and Javi's future is up in the air.

-1.title: Law and Disorder
-1.plot: Step into the courtroom as we recount the top 10 custody battles, arrests, and 911 worthy moments from TM2 that had you gasping for air.

imdb.plot outline: A spin-off of the MTV documentary series '16 and Pregnant'. The show follows the stories of four girls from the second season of '16 and Pregnant' and documents the challenges of their first years of motherhood. Each episode interweaves stories of four teenage girls who are navigating the bumpy terrain of adolescence, growing pains, and coming of age - all while facing the responsibility of being a young mother. Each story offers a unique look into the wide variety of challenges young mothers can face: marriage, relationships, family support, or lack thereof, adoption, finances, rumors among the community, graduating high school, starting college, getting (or losing) a job and the daunting and exciting step of moving out of the nest to create their own families.
imdb.title: Teen Mom 2
plot: Follows the cast of the second season of '16 and Pregnant', giving viewers an intimate look at the challenges Chelsea, Leah, Jenelle, and Kailyn face raising a child as a teenager.::Anonymous
